1.0.0.name: wordpress/simple-meta-tags
1.0.0.description:
Allows you to set global meta tags and customize on each individual page/post.

The plugin will generat the blog title and page title as default title tags if not specified otherwise.

For backwards compatibility, if this section is missing, the full length of the short description will be used, and Markdown parsed.
